	<id>cockatrice.desktop</id>
	<name>Cockatrice</name>
	<summary>Virtual tabletop for multiplayer card games</summary>
	<developer_name>Cockatrice Project</developer_name>
	<description>
		<p>
		Cockatrice is an open-source multi-platform supported program for playing tabletop card games over a network. 
		The program's server design prevents any kind of client modifications to gain an unfair advantage in a game. 
		The client also has a built in single-player mode where you can create decks without being connected to a server.
		</p>
